'''依泊二醇'''（{{lang-en|'''Epomediol'''}}，商品名'''Clesidren'''）是一种人工合成的[[类萜|类萜]]物质，分子式[[C10H18O3|C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>18</sub>O<sub>3</sub>]]，有{{le|利胆剂|Choleretic}}的作用，可用于[[对症治疗|对症治疗]]{{le|妊娠期肝内胆汁淤积|Intrahepatic cholestasis of pregnancy}}引起的骚[[癢|癢]]。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Gonzalez MC, Iglesias J, Tiribelli C |title=Epomediol ameliorates pruritus in patients with intrahepatic cholestasis of pregnancy |journal=J Hepatol |volume=16 |issue=1–2 |pages=241–2 |date=September 1992 |pmid=1484159 |doi= 10.1016/S0168-8278(05)80122-9|display-authors=etal}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Reyes H |title=The spectrum of liver and gastrointestinal disease seen in cholestasis of pregnancy |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_gastroenterology-clinics-of-north-america_1992-12_21_4/page/905 |journal=Gastroenterol Clin North Am |volume=21 |issue=4 |pages=905–21 |date=December 1992 |pmid=1478743 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Reyes H, Simon FR |title=Intrahepatic cholestasis of pregnancy: an estrogen-related disease |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_seminars-in-liver-disease_1993-08_13_3/page/289 |journal=Semin Liver Dis |volume=13 |issue=3 |pages=289–301 |date=August 1993 |pmid=8235718 |doi= 10.1055/s-2007-1007357}}</ref>

